  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[struct WindowSystemInfoWin32 : public IRenderer::WindowSystemInfoBase;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>WindowSystemInfoWin32</TypeRef> structure identifies the Win32 window system during renderer initialization.
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
      Availability: Windows when <TypeRef>COBALT_RENDERER_WIN32_SUPPORT</TypeRef> is enabled. This is automatically enabled on Windows unless platform binding selection is manual.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Members">
    <Paragraph>
      This structure has no public fields beyond the inherited base structure fields.
